data.description: UPGRADES ! New Roof 2022,  New Paint Throughout Interior of Home to include Walls, Ceilings, Doors & Trim / New Wood-Look Tile Throughout House / New Garage Door and Opener / New Kitchen Faucet. This Affordable Home with a Great Location in South Crestview ! The Living Room has Raised Ceiling, Fireplace, Plant Ledge and Fiberglass French Doors which lead to the Backyard. The Kitchen has Granite Counter tops, White Cabinets and White Appliances. The Bedroom Floorplan has Good Room Sizes and Closets. The backyard has Plenty of Potential to Make it a Great Entertainment Area. Seller will Pay $6K toward Buyers Closing with Full Price offer ! Great Corner Lot !  Make your Appointment Today ~  ROOF: 2022     AC: 2020
